### Create a deck
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/decks
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Biology Deck" }

### List decks
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/decks

### Create a card in a deck (basic)
# replace :deckId after creating a deck
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/decks/:deckId/cards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "basic",
  "prompt": "What is the powerhouse of the cell?",
  "answer": "Mitochondria"
}

### Create a card from a DocBlock (optional)
# replace :deckId and :blockId
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/decks/:deckId/cards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "basic",
  "prompt": "Summarize this point",
  "answer": "ATP synthesis",
  "blockId": ":blockId"
}

### List cards in deck
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/decks/:deckId/cards

### Get due cards for study
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/decks/:deckId/due

### Review a card (again | gotit)
# replace :cardId
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/cards/:cardId/review
Content-Type: application/json

{ "result": "gotit" }
